snippet: Land brokers and development companies in the Minneapolis-St. Paul area are reporting that after years of no growth, the price of land is increasing rapidly.
abstract: Latest land rush is in full swing in Minneapolis-St Paul area, where brokers and development companies are reporting price of land is increasing rapidly, following years of no growth; developers are reporting that, for first time, they are seeing cities work to help them navigate zoning, permitting and mapping pipeline, even relaxing zoning rules and lowering fees to encourage development and get construction started.
lead_paragraph: Land brokers and development companies in the Minneapolis-St. Paul area are reporting that after years of no growth, the price of land is increasing rapidly.

headline.main: Prices Are Rising for New Homes, and the Land They Are Built On
headline.print_headline: Prices Are Rising for New Homes, and the Land They Are Built On
